The best bang for your buck for tattoo fonts. Hands down. My one and only dislike of this amazing app is that it doesn't have to option to add curvature to the script. That being said, the best part is when you upgrade to the pro version you really get a vast amount of fonts. Every client has always found one they like. A must have for tattoo artists.

Opened this for the first time and straight away it asks for a rating. At least give me a chance to use it first so I have an idea to see what it's like. I'll rate again when I've had a chance to use it. Edit: The banner still comes up EVERY time, and it covers almost half my screen. Once you've rated, I don't see why it should continue to come up after that.
replyContent:
Hello,

First, thanks for your comment. "Rate this app" banner is on the save page. But you are not obliged to rate the app to save your design. You can save your design without rating the app. It is not a full screen and  irrefutable offer. It's just a simple banner on the bottom of the page.
